content:
IWithAppServicePlan Interface

Definition

A web app update allowing app service plan to be set.

In this Article

public interface IWithAppServicePlan

Methods

WithExistingAppServicePlan(IAppServicePlan)

Uses an existing app service plan for the web app.
WithNewAppServicePlan(String)

Creates a new app service plan to use.
